n%20Reddit%20and%20other%20social%20media%20spurred%20retail%20traders%20to%20pile%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDay%20traders%20have%20Microsoft%20and%20Meta%20%26quot%3Bto%20play%20with%20for%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Gross%20said.%20The%20tech%20titans%20are%20up%2030%25%20and%2025%25%20respectively%20this%20year%20because%20of%20AI%20excitement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220adcac0a-73ac-4e6f-9aad-1868c157ad26%5C%22%3EGross%20says%20GameStop%20isn't%20acting%20like%20a%20meme%20stock%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGross%20%E2%80%94%20known%20as%20the%20%26quot%3BBond%20King%26quot%3B%20for%20growing%20fixed-income%20titan%20PIMCO's%20flagship%20Total%20Return%20Fund%20to%20%24270%20billion%20over%20nearly%2030%20years%20%E2%80%94%20said%20the%20stock%20that%20started%20it%20all%2C%20GameStop%2C%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20behaving%20like%20a%20meme%26quot%3B%20and%20is%20%26quot%3Bmuch%20less%20volatile%26quot%3B%20than%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20he%20still%20viewed%20it%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bgood%20candidate%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-is-options-trading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eoption%20selling%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGross%20said%20the%20stock%20%26quot%3Bseems%20to%20mimic%20bitcoin%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20most%20valuable%20cryptocurrency%2C%20known%20for%20its%20volatility%20and%20passionate%20fanbase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBitcoin's%20price%20fell%20by%20a%20quarter%20between%20early%20January%20and%20early%20April%20this%20year%2C%20but%20has%20rallied%20to%20record%20highs%20of%20above%20%24110%2C000.%20GameStop%20announced%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgamestop-bitcoin-price-investment-strategy-trump-media-djt-gme-metaplanet-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efirst%20bitcoin%20purchase%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20late%20May%2C%20securing%204%2C710%20tokens%20worth%20around%20%24537%20million%20at%20current%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdjusted%20for%20a%20stock%20split%20in%202022%2C%20GameStop%20soared%20from%20around%20%241%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202020%20to%20a%20peak%20intraday%20price%20of%20%24121%20on%20January%2028%2C%202021.%20It%20has%20traded%20within%20a%20much%20tighter%20range%20of%20around%20%2420%20to%20%2435%20over%20the%20past%2012%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20followed%20a%20similar%20trajectory%20to%20bitcoin%20by%20rising%20sharply%20in%20the%20fourth%20quarter%20of%202024%2C%20slumping%20this%20spring%2C%20and%20rebounding%20through%20early%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20GameStop%20then%20fell%20after%20disappointing%20first-quarter%20earnings%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fgamestop-stock-profits-share-sale-cash-pile-raoaring-kitty-gme-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edilutive%20share%20sales%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20whereas%20bitcoin%20kept%20climbing%20to%20fresh%20highs%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGross%20bet%20against%20GameStop%20by%20selling%20call%20options%20at%20the%20height%20of%20its%20meme-stock%20surge%20in%20January%202021.%20An%20options%20contract%20gives%20the%20buyer%20the%20right%20to%20purchase%20or%20sell%20a%20stock%20at%20an%20agreed%20price%20within%20a%20set%20period.%20Sellers%20wager%20these%20contracts%20will%20expire%20worthless%2C%20and%20they%20can%20simply%20keep%20the%20premium%20paid%20by%20the%20buyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGross%20was%20%2415%20million%20in%20the%20red%2C%20losing%20sleep%20at%20one%20point%20as%20GameStop%20kept%20climbing%2C%20but%20he%20doubled%20down.%20He%20later%20said%20he%20made%20between%20%2415%20million%20and%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2420%20million%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fbill-gross-lost-money-meme-stocks-now-up-20-million-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebetting%20against%20GameStop%20and%20AMC%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20knew%20I%20had%20an%20advantage%20over%20Reddit%20and%20the%20bo