20it%20could%20get%2C%20but%20the%20NFL%20thinks%20it%20can%20get%20even%20more%20money%20by%20taking%20one%20package%20of%20games%20and%20turning%20it%20into%20multiple%20packages%20it%20can%20sell%20to%20multiple%20owners.%20(For%20the%20record%3A%20Both%20Disney%20and%20the%20NFL%20note%20that%20Disney%20will%20take%20some%20Monday%20night%20games%20it%20was%20already%20showing%20and%20turn%20those%20into%20games%20on%20the%20NFL%20Network%2C%20so%20it%20will%20still%20show%20seven%20games%20via%20that%20channel.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20that's%20what%20the%20NFL%20has%20been%20doing%20for%20years%3A%20Slicing%20and%20re-slicing%20its%20game%20rights%2C%20and%20selling%20them%20to%20a%20growing%20list%20of%20buyers.%20In%202021%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2021%2F03%2F18%2Fnfl-media-rights-deal-2023-2033-amazon-gets-exclusive-thursday-night.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%3C%2Fa%3E%20signed%20a%20deal%20to%20stream%20Thursday%20night%20games%20for%20about%20%241%20billion%20a%20year.%20Now%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-nfl-football-streaming-deal-explained-peter-kafka-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENetflix%20has%20a%20deal%20to%20show%20two%20games%20on%20Christmas.%3C%2Fa%3E%20And%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D111a836d2647effbc8a528a1b41f962cab11053b618e02d1740f0b6ab096684f%26postID%3D6893459145129e7dc8d5bdd8%26postSlug%3Ddisney-nfl-deal-shows-who-owns-tv-2025-8%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.nfl.com%252Fnews%252Fyoutube-to-stream-2025-week-1-nfl-regular-season-game-in-brazil-to-worldwide-audience-for-free%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20stream%20the%20first%20game%20of%20the%20season%20next%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20wrote%20last%20October%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnfl-network-sale-paramount-youtube-espn-2024-10%5C%22%2