%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%2028-year-old%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20just%2024%2C%20the%20economics%20graduate%20started%20her%20farming%20career%20with%20English%20cucumbers.%20In%20her%20first%20harvest%2C%20she%20achieved%20an%20impressive%20yield%20of%2051%20tonnes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20nearly%20three%20times%20the%20yield%20that%20traditional%20farmers%20receive%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBuoyed%20by%20her%20initial%20success%2C%20she%20then%20cultivated%20red%20and%20yellow%20bell%20peppers%2C%20which%20also%20thrived.%20On%20one%20acre%20of%20land%2C%20she%20yielded%2035%20tonnes%20of%20bell%20peppers%2C%20selling%20for%20an%20average%20price%20of%20Rs%2080-100%20per%20kilo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-95-min-1729257171.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Protected%20cultivation%20involves%20regulating%20factors%20like%20temperature%2C%20humidity%2C%20and%20light%20in%20a%20controlled%20environment.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-95-min-1729257171.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-95-min-1729257171-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-95-min-1729257171-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-95-min-1729257171-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-95-min-1729257171-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-371253%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EProtected%20cultivation%20involves%20regulating%20factors%20like%20temperature%2C%20humidity%2C%20and%20light%20in%20a%20controlled%20environment%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20her%20polyhouse%20flourished%2C%20she%20leased%20an%20additional%20five%20acres%2C%20diversifying%20her%20crops%20to%20include%20many%20exotic%20vegetables%20such%20as%20lettuce%2C%20bok%20choy%2C%20zucchini%2C%20kale%2C%20parsley%2C%20and%20red%20cabbage.%20She%20has%20also%20launched%20a%20nursery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20harvest%20time%20for%20each%20vegetable%20varies.%20Bell%20peppers%20have%20a%2010%20month%20crop%20cycle%2C%20cucumbers%20take%20three%20to%20four%20months%2C%20salad%20vegetables%20mature%20in%2045%20days%2C%20and%20zucchinis%20require%20about%20four%20months.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20she%20produces%20almost%20210%20tonnes%20of%20bell%20peppers%20every%20year.%20Apart%20from%20being%20sold%20on%20quick%20commerce%20platforms%2C%20her%20vegetables%20also%20make%20their%20way%20to%20wholesale%20markets%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Varanasi%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20turnover%20of%20Rs%201%20crore.%20She%20employs%2025-30%20workers%2C%20predominantly%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20most%20important%2C%20Anushka%20says%2C%20is%20to%20let%20the%20land%20rest%20periodically%20to%20enhance%20its%20productivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20solarise%20the%20land%20for%20two%20months%20each%20year%2C%20May%20and%20June%2C%20to%20harness%20the%20sun%E2%80%99s%20energy.%20The%20process%20involves%20covering%20the%20soil%20to%20let%20it%20breathe.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20use%20chemicals%3B%20instead%2C%20we%20add%20manure%20to%20tackle%20soil-borne%20diseases%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98People%20didn%E2%80%99t%20take%20me%20seriously%20as%20I%20am%20a%20woman%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20young%20farmer%20has%20quickly%20gained%20recognition%20in%20Lucknow%20and%20nearby%20ci