2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalt-disney-surprising-facts-trivia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDisney%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20it's%20pressing%20ahead%20to%20fully%20integrate%20Hulu%20into%20Disney%2B%20for%20all%20subscribers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDisney%20plans%20to%20launch%20a%20unified%20streaming%20app%20for%20Disney%2B%20and%20Hulu%20next%20year.%20In%20international%20markets%2C%20Hulu%20will%20replace%20the%20Star%20tile%20on%20the%20Disney%2B%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20news%2C%20announced%20during%20its%20quarterly%20earnings%2C%20came%20after%20Disney%20finalized%20a%20plan%20last%20month%20to%20take%20full%20ownership%20of%20Hulu%2C%20buying%20out%20Comcast's%20one-third%20stake.%20Disney%20first%20became%20a%20Hulu%20shareholder%20in%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plans%20give%20further%20credence%20to%20speculation%20among%20Disney%20streaming%20insiders%20that%20Disney%20might%20eventually%20phase%20out%20the%20Hulu%20app.%20Business%20Insider's%20James%20Faris%20reported%20this%20week%20that%20it%20had%20become%20impossible%20to%20ignore%20the%20Mouse%20House's%20increasing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-hulu-future-streaming-employees-ad-revenue-growth-espn-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eemphasis%20on%20Disney%2B%20over%20Hulu%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDisney%20execs%20didn't%20directly%20comment%20about%20the%20future%20of%20the%20stand-alone%20Hulu%20app%20when%20asked%20about%20it%20on%20Wednesday's%20earnings%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDisney%20merged%20the%20ad%20servers%20for%20Disney%2B%20and%20Hulu%20together%20for%20the%20first%20time%20last%20week%2C%20two%20Disney%20streaming%20employees%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20Creating%20a%20unified%20ad%20server%2C%20known%20internally%20as%20%26quot%3BMission%20Control%2C%26quot%3B%20was%20a%20painstaking%20but%20crucial%20step%20to%20building%20a%20streaming%20super%20app%2C%20these%20employees%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverything%20going%20through%20one%20ad%20server%20makes%20a%20lot%20less%20work%20for%20everyone%20involved%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20getting%20ad%20campaigns%20live%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20employees%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearch%20firm%20MoffettNathanson's%20Robert%20Fishman%20wrote%20in%20a%20mid-July%20note%20that%20further%20integrating%20Hulu%20into%20Disney%2B%20could%20save%20the%20company%20about%20%243%20billion%20through%20%26quot%3Bthe%20elimination%20of%20duplicative%20technology%20and%20administrative%20costs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20on%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWednesday%20from%20Disney%20CEO%20Bob%20Iger%20and%20its%20chief%20financial%20officer%2C%20Hugh%20Johnston%2C%20the%20executives%20said%20the%20merging%20of%20Hulu%20into%20Disney%2B%20would%20give%20subscribers%20more%20choice%20and%20personalization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20will%20enhance%20our%20ability%20to%20continue%20to%20grow%20profitability%20and%20margins%20in%20our%20entertainment%20streaming%20business%20through%20expected%20higher%20engagement%2C%20lower%20churn%2C%20and%20advertising%20revenue%20potential%2C%20as%20well%20as%20operational%20efficiencies%20that%20over%20time%20may%20result%20in%20savings%20that%20we%20can%20reinvest%20back%20into%20the%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDisney%20had%20already%20been%20steering%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-plus-hulu-content-parent-controls-kid-accounts-pg-rating-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ebundle%20subscribers%20to%20the%20Disney%2B%20app%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20loading%20it%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewith%20most%20Hulu%20movies%20and%20shows%20and%20some%20ESPN%20content.%20Unbundled%20Disney%20subscribers%20can%20also%20watch%20some%20Hulu%20and%20ESPN%20shows%20free%20of%20charge%20on%20Disney%2B.%20But%20Disney%2B%20content%20isn't%2