5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dubapp.com%2Fdubreport%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Great%20Wealth%20Reset%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%202025%20report%20conducted%20by%20The%20Harris%20Poll%20on%20behalf%20of%20dub%20among%202%2C000%20US%20adults%2C%20Gen%20Z%20(ages%2018%20to%2028)%20say%20the%20ideal%20age%20for%20achieving%20financial%20independence%20is%2032.%20As%20for%20when%20they'd%20like%20to%20actually%20hit%20that%20milestone%2C%2094%25%20say%20they%20want%20to%20be%20there%20no%20later%20than%20age%2055.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20they%20aren't%20relying%20on%20a%209-to-5%20to%20accelerate%20their%20lofty%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20survey%20found%20that%2060%25%20of%20Gen%20Z%20believe%20a%20traditional%20job%20won't%20help%20them%20reach%20their%20financial%20goals.%20Instead%2C%20they're%20banking%20on%20side%20hustles%2C%20freelance%20work%2C%20and%20entrepreneurship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYoung%20Americans%20aren't%20rejecting%20the%20idea%20of%20wealth%2C%20they're%20recreating%20the%20path%20to%20get%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Steven%20Wang%2C%20the%20Gen%20Z%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20investing%20app%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dubapp.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edub%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20why%20they're%20more%20inclined%20to%20take%20a%20less%20traditional%20path%2C%20Wang%20points%20to%20a%20few%20reasons.%20First%2C%20there%20are%20more%20digital%20opportunities%20than%20ever%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BExpressing%20yourself%20as%20a%20creator%2C%20potentially%20going%20viral%2C%20and%20making%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20through%20that%20%E2%80%94%20that%20was%20impossible%2010%20years%20ago%2C%20but%20nowadays%2C%20because%20of%20social%20media%2C%20web%202.0%2C%20I%20think%20that%20will%20only%20accelerate%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20points%20to%20a%20general%20feeling%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bloss%20of%20trust%20in%20the%20future%20and%20the%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20His%20generation%20is%20paying%20attention%20to%20data%20points%20such%20as%20the%20growing%20wealth%20gap%20and%20rapid%20inflation.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20deteriorated%20the%20belief%20in%20the%20institutions%20that%20got%20us%20where%20we%20are%20today%2C%20and%20worked%20for%20our%20parents.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20%26quot%3Bthere's%20this%20'going%20against%20the%20grain'%20sentiment%20that%20I%20think%20my%20generation%20can%20really%20get%20behind.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVal%20Zapata%20is%20just%20one%20example%20of%20Gen%20Zers%20building%20wealth%20on%20their%20own%20terms.%20She%20turned%20her%20sneaker-collecting%20hobby%20into%20a%20side%20hustle%20and%2C%20eventually%2C%20a%20full-time%20gig.%20She%20now%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-a-gen-z-entrepreneur-built-seven-figure-resale-business-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esells%20millions%20of%20dollars%20worth%20of%20sneakers%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20streetwear%20by%20hosting%20live%20shows%20through%20the%20platform%20Whatnot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZapata%20immigrated%20from%20Colombia%20as%20a%20kid%2C%20grew%20up%20in%20New%20York%20and%20Texas%2C%20and%20didn't%20go%20to%20college.%20She%20used%20online%20resources%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20scale%20her%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20learned%20everything%20about%20resale%20on%20YouTube%20for%20free%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20including%20how%20to%20scale%20her%20Instagram%20account%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftheshoe.gameco%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Shoe%20Game%20Co.%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20how%20to%20set%20up%20a%20Whatnot%20show%2C%20which%20is%20where%20the%20majority%20of%20her%20sales%20come%20from.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20generation%20is%20leaning%20into%20free%20resources%20offered%20through%20social%20media%20platforms%20much%20more%20than%20other%20generations.%20The%