0%9D%20he%20smiled%2C%20promising%20to%20return%20it%20on%20his%20next%20trip.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20simple%20act%20%E2%80%94%20but%20one%20that%20ties%20strangers%20together%20through%20stories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20story%20you%20can%20add%20to%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20live%20in%20an%20age%20of%20screens%20and%20scrolling%2C%20where%20the%20habit%20of%20reading%20feels%20like%20it%E2%80%99s%20slipping%20away.%20For%20children%2C%20especially%2C%20imagination%20often%20comes%20second%20to%20instant%20entertainment.%20The%20Flybrary%20gently%20pushes%20back%20against%20that%20trend.%20It%20says%20books%20still%20matter%3B%20that%20stories%20still%20have%20the%20power%20to%20pause%20us%2C%20comfort%20us%2C%20and%20make%20the%20world%20feel%20less%20lonely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20something%20special%20about%20holding%20a%20book%20that%20has%20passed%20through%20other%20hands%20%E2%80%94%20hands%20that%20turned%20these%20very%20pages%20on%20other%20journeys%2C%20in%20other%20moments.%20That%E2%80%99s%20what%20makes%20the%20Flybrary%20more%20than%20just%20a%20shelf.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20chain%20of%20generosity%2C%20stitched%20together%20by%20people%20who%20believe%20in%20sharing%20something%20as%20simple%20and%20beautiful%20as%20a%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20next%20time%20you%20pack%20for%20a%20flight%2C%20slip%20in%20an%20extra%20one.%20Leave%20it%20on%20the%20shelf%20before%20you%20board.%20Somewhere%2C%20someone%20will%20find%20it%20exactly%20when%20they%20need%20it%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1754401488000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1754400933.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D481918%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20Bhubaneswar%20Airport%2C%20two%20shelves%20of%20books%20are%20making%20travel%20softer%20and%20kinder.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20how%20Flybrary%20runs%20on%20trust%20and%20love%20for%20stories.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sanjna%20Nair%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F481918%2Fflybrary-bhubaneswar-airport-free-library-books%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Mumbai%20Mum%20Is%20Making%20Travel%20With%20Kids%20Fun%2C%20Easy%20%26amp%3B%20Nature-Filled%20With%20Her%20Curated%20Treks%20and%20Trails%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20reporting%20and%20writing%20for%20this%20story%20were%20originally%20done%20in%20September%202024%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20weekend%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20embarked%20on%20an%20exhilarating%20hike%20with%20our%201.5-year-old%20son.%20We%20set%20off%20at%205%20am%20to%20reach%20the%20village%20of%20Bhutivali%2C%20near%20Karjat.%20After%20enjoying%20breakfast%20at%20a%20local%E2%80%99s%20home%2C%20we%20began%20our%20trek%2C%20crossing%20a%20serene%20lake%20en%20route%20to%20a%20waterfall.%20The%20sight%20of%20the%20picturesque%20lake%20was%20a%20true%20feast%20for%20the%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20took%20turns%20carrying%20our%20son%2C%20a%20light%20drizzle%20energised%20us.%20After%20nearly%20an%20hour%20and%20a%20half%2C%20we%20reached%20the%20waterfall%20and%20knew%20the%20effort%20was%20well%20worth%20it.%20Watching%20our%20son%20delight%20in%20the%20water%2C%20chase%20butterflies%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F325192%2Fsaakshi-gulati-nikita-mathur-travel-with-kids-india-plan-vacations-for-moms-kids-toddlers-baby%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplay%20with%20other%20children%20%3C%2Fa%3Ereminded%20us%20that%20some%20experiences%20are%20priceless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20enjoying%20some%20hot%20Maggi%20and%20tea%20near%20the%20waterfall%2C%20we%20started%20our%20return%20journey%2C%20only%20to%20be%20greeted%20by%20a%20herd%20of%20cows%20and%20buffaloes.%20Our%20son%20was%20completely%20captivated%2C%20sitting%20and%20watching%20them%20for%20several%20minutes.%20We%20eventually%20had%20to%20coax%20him%20away%20with%20a%20promise%20to%20bring%20him%20back!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20returned%20home%20that%20evening%2C%20our%20hearts%20full%20and%20our%20pockets%20brimming%20with%20unforgettable%20memories%2C%20realising%20what%20we%20had%20been%20missing%20all%20along.%20Our%20son%20had%20made%20new%20friends%20%E2%80%94%20hens%2C%20cows%2C%20butterflies%2C%20and%20swans%20%E2%80%94%20and%20those%20simple%20moments%20made%20the%20day%20truly%20special.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20increasingly%20digital%20world%20where%20children%20are%20often%20glued%20to%20screens%2C%20introducing%20them%20to%20nature%20has%20never%20been%20more%20important.%20Nehal%20Shah%20realised%20this%20after%20becoming%20a%20mother.%20As%20an%20avid%20trekker%2C%20she%20sought%20out%20places%20and%20trips%20suitable%20for%20her%20infant%2C%20but%20her%20searches%20only%20led%20to%20indoor%20activities.%20Frustrated%20by%20the%20lack%20of%20outdoor%20options%20for%20young%20children%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20create%20something%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnehal-shah-1726490018.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nehal%20with%20her%20family%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnehal-shah-1726490018.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnehal-shah-1726490018-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnehal-shah-1726490018-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnehal-shah-1726490018-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads