eless%20monuments%2C%20but%20also%20the%20everyday%20stories%20that%20give%20it%20soul%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKumail%2C%20also%20a%20native%20of%20Lucknow%2C%20has%20known%20Taqi%20since%20childhood.%20However%2C%20neither%20of%20them%20imagined%20that%20one%20day%20they%20would%20end%20up%20working%20together.%20With%20a%20strong%20background%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F334375%2Fnancy-tyagi-instagram-fashion-influencer-inspiring-youtuber-uttar-pradesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ephotography%2C%20videography%2C%20and%20direction%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Kumail%20has%20collaborated%20with%20major%20production%20houses%20like%20Red%20Chillies%20Entertainment%20and%20Zee%20Studios.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20freelancing%20for%20a%20while%2C%20I%20moved%20back%20to%20Lucknow%20in%202018.%20From%20short%20films%20to%20documentaries%2C%20I%20worked%20on%20a%20range%20of%20projects%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20in%20touch%20with%20Taqi%20then%2C%20but%20when%20he%20started%20%3Cem%3ELucknow%20Uncovered%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20I%20came%20across%20his%20page%20and%20I%20appreciated%20the%20content.%20Although%20I%20was%20never%20a%20fan%20of%20vertical%20filmmaking%2C%20especially%20the%20kind%20you%20see%20on%20Instagram%20Reels%2C%20I%20ended%20up%20doing%20my%20first%20vertical%20video%20with%20him%2C%20mainly%20because%20every%20time%20he%20comes%20to%20a%20shoot%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20clear%20that%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20solid%20vision%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20research%20behind%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-04T142700.004-1754297887.jpg%5C%22%20width%