ming%20pool%20using%20nothing%20but%20natural%20materials%20%E2%80%94%20no%20cement%2C%20no%20chemicals.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Srimoyee%20Chowdhury%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Escape%20City%20Life%20in%20This%20Fairytale%20Mud%20Home%20in%20Rishikesh%2C%20Built%20by%2090%20People%20From%2018%20Countries%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFeatured%20image%20courtesy%3A%20Atik%20Bheda%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20interviews%20and%20reporting%20for%20this%20feature%20were%20conducted%20in%202024.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20do%20you%20mean%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20a%20replica%20of%20Hagrid%E2%80%99s%20house%3F%E2%80%9D%20I%20ask%20Raghav%20Kumar%20(30)%2C%20one%20half%20of%20the%20brother%20duo%20that%20has%20conceptualised%20a%20600-sq%20ft%20beauty%20in%20the%20heartland%20of%20Rishikesh%2C%20Uttarakhand.%20As%20fans%20of%20the%20seven-part%20fantasy%20series%20%E2%80%98Harry%20Potter%E2%80%99%20will%20immediately%20guess%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20referring%20to%20the%20eight-foot-tall%20giant%20Rubeus%20Hagrid%E2%80%99s%20cabin%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20The%20Forbidden%20Forest%20%E2%80%94%20an%20ominous%20wood%20filled%20with%20wizarding%20creatures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECosy%20fires%2C%20larger-than-life%20teacups%2C%20and%20a%20drooling%20boarhound%20Fang%20filled%20most%20evenings%20that%20Harry%20and%20his%20friends%20spent%20at%20Hagrid%E2%80%99s.%20I%20often%20found%20myself%20craving%20to%20be%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20wish%20might%20just%20have%20been%20answered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaghav%20and%20Ansh%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Tiny%20Farm%20Fort%E2%80%99%20is%20reminiscent%20of%20Hagrid%E2%80%99s%20abode.%20Creating%20the%2015-ft%20doppelganger%20homestay%2C%20the%20brothers%20say%2C%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20goal%20that%20backed%20their%20transition%20from%20their%20city%20life%20in%20Delhi%20to%20the%20mountains%20in%202021.%20Instead%2C%20it%20was%20a%20consequence%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20architects%2C%20Raghav%20and%20Ansh%20(27)%20were%20keen%20on%20living%20an%20%E2%80%9Cintentional%20life%20closer%20to%20nature%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20a%20dream%20they%20felt%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20achieved%20by%20being%20a%20part%20of%20modern%20corporate%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F247572%2Fmaharashtra-ecofriendly-green-architecture-domes-arches-cost-effective-sustainable-homes-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earchitectural%20projects%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20prized%20demand%20over%20sustainability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20disconnect%20between%20the%20architect%20and%20the%20labour%20involved%20in%20these%20projects.%20There%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20greenwashing%2C%E2%80%9D%20Raghav%20notes.%20Prior%20to%202021%2C%20the%20Delhi-based%20boys%20had%20their%20week%20cut%20out%20for%20them%20%E2%80%94%20weekdays%20spent%20working%20long%20hours%20and%20weekends%20trekking%20to%20North%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F9_3aPdHLQ9Y%3Fsi%3DuSBCfoXQnBlYuCgm%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seed%20for%20Tiny%20Farm%20Fort%20was%20sown%20when%2C%20after%20one%20particular%20trek%20to%20Rishikesh%20in%20December%202020%2C%20Raghav%20and%20Ansh%20found%20themselves%20wishing%20they%20could%20stay%20back%20in%20the%20mountains%20and%20not%20return%20to%20the%20monotonous%20hustle.%20And%20they%20decided%20to%20do%20just%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20completely%20bewildered%20by%20topics%20of%20gardening%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F189744%2Fbangalore-lifestyle-one-day-hol