nts%2C%20animals%20and%20insects%20help%20each%20other%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20only%20when%20people%20stop%20interfering%20with%20the%20system%20that%20they%E2%80%99ll%20see%20signs%20of%20growth.%E2%80%9D%20But%20she%20emphasises%20that%20present-day%20pesticides%20and%20chemicals%20are%20the%20culprits%2C%20killing%20the%20heart%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F329567%2Fmumbai-homestay-with-organic-farming-food-forest-sustainable-vacation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%20ecosystem%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20the%20microbes%20in%20the%20soil.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsustainable-homestay-4-1721041200.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20ingredients%20for%20the%20meals%20at%20Adiem%20Kaanan%20Farmstay%20are%20sourced%20from%20the%20land%20are%20are%20fresh%2C%20healthy%20and%20delicious%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsustainable-homestay-4-1721041200.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsustainable-homestay-4-1721041200-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsustainable-homestay-4-1721041200-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsustainable-homestay-4-1721041200-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsustainable-homestay-4-1721041200-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-356902%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20ingredients%20for%20the%20meals%20at%20Adiem%20Kaanan%20Farmstay%20are%20sourced%20from%20the%20land%20are%20are%