2%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Adiem%20Kaanan%20Farmstay%20sits%20on%20a%20six-acre%20piece%20of%20land%20that%20also%20boasts%20rainwater%20harvesting%20and%20solar%20panels%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Disha%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDrawing%20parallels%20with%20the%20change%20in%20mindset%20living%20on%20a%20farm%20has%20brought%20about%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20younger%20and%20saw%20my%20parents%20lead%20a%20sustainable%20life%2C%20I%20did%20not%20understand%20their%20reasons%20for%20these%20choices.%20I%20was%20always%20chasing%20life%20in%20a%20big%20city%2C%20a%20big%20house%2C%20a%20big%20car%2C%20etc.%20But%20during%20my%20time%20in%20the%20corporate%20world%2C%20I%20could%20see%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20supply%20chains%20first-hand%20and%20how%20robotic%20it%20was.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20growing%20her%20own%20food%20feels%20like%20a%20treat%20to%20the%20senses.%20%E2%80%9CI%20can%E2%80%99t%20even%20express%20how%20freeing%20it%20feels.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdiem%20Farmstay%20boasts%20two%20cottages%20%E2%80%94%20a%20two-bedroom%20villa%20and%20a%20one-bedroom%20villa.%20The%20farmstay%20is%20powered%20by%20solar%20energy%20and%20has%20a%20brilliantly%20designed%20rainwater%20harvesting%20system.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20system%E2%80%99s%20capacity%20is%2032%2C000%20litres%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Madhu.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20dependent%20on%20rainwater%20for%20our%20day-to-day%20needs%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F290271%2Fmumbai-rain-man-makes-rainwater-harvesting-system-using-low-cost-innovation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eharvest%20every%20drop%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20do%20not%20depend%20on%20the%20government%20at%20all.%20In%20fact%2C%20we%20give%20the%20government%20approximately%201%2C200%20units%20every%20month.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp